Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human pose estimation from 2D images. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper involves fitting a 3D body model to 2D observations. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses a deep network for direct estimation of model parameters. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image-based human pose estimation. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the paper involves fitting a body model to 2D joints, which can be useful for robotics applications.
